{"sectionId":51,"sectionIdLiteral":"051","humanId":"text-intro","volumeId":"text","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"superTitle":"Text","title":"Introduction"},"annotation":"T-in","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text text-intro\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"051#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>This is a course in miracles.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>It is a required course.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Only the time you take it is voluntary.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Free will does not mean that you can establish the curriculum.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>It means only that you can elect what you want to take at a given time.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>The course does not aim at teaching the meaning of love, for that is beyond what can be taught.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>It does aim, however, at removing the blocks to the awareness of love’s presence, which is your natural inheritance.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#1:8\"><span class=\"snr\">8</span>The opposite of love is fear, but what is all-encompassing can have no opposite.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"051#2\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>This course can therefore be summed up very simply in this way:</span></p> <p class=\"p-bold p-italic p-prayer\"><span data-sentence-id=\"051#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Nothing real can be threatened.<br/></span> <span data-sentence-id=\"051#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Nothing unreal exists.</span></p> <p class=\"p-italic\"><span data-sentence-id=\"051#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Herein lies the peace of God.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"This is a course in miracles. It is a required course. Only the time you take it is voluntary. Free will does not mean that you can establish the curriculum. It means only that you can elect what you","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Text: Introduction | ACIM","seoDescription":"✨ A Course in Miracles. Read “Text: Introduction” from the Text (T-in): This is a course in miracles. It is a required course. Only the time you take it is voluntary. Free will does not…","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Text","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":51,"slugs":["text","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Introduction","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":51,"slugs":["text","introduction"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Text","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":51,"slugs":["text","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Introduction","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":51,"slugs":["text","introduction"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Text","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":51,"slugs":["text","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Introduction","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":51,"slugs":["text","introduction"]}}],"slugs":["text","introduction"],"canonicalLink":"https://acim.org/acim/text/introduction/en/s/51","link":"https://acim.org/acim/text/introduction/en/s/51","shortLink":"https://acim.org/acim/en/s/51","previousSectionId":43,"previousSectionSlugs":["preface","what-it-says"],"previousSectionLink":"https://acim.org/acim/preface/what-it-says/en/s/43","nextSectionId":53,"nextSectionSlugs":["chapter-1","principles-of-miracles"],"nextSectionLink":"https://acim.org/acim/chapter-1/principles-of-miracles/en/s/53","hreflangLinks":[{"hrefLang":"en","link":"https://acim.org/acim/en/s/51"}]}